newsitem.title: USA: Iowa State Board of Regents won by Smith Barney.
newsitem.headline: Iowa State Board of Regents won by Smith Barney.

text.p: Smith Barney Inc said it won $7.615 million of Iowa State Board of Regents, telecommunications facilities revenue bonds, Series I.S.U. 1997, with a true interest cost of 4.34 percent.
